ck_adapt integrates adapt.js (see https://github.com/nathansmith/adapt ) into Contao cms as a module.

In fact, Contao will generate an 960.gs-based output on the fly

=====

For more information, see...

http://adapt.960.gs

This is dual licensed under GPL and MIT.

Feel free to use it however you like. :)

=====

Feedback, issues: Please use ticketing system at http://contao-forge.org/projects/ckadapt